text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text: What's this!? Trainer has made a……mistake!?

text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text: No, no, there's a saying that says you'll succeed one day if you just try!

text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text: I've hit telephone poles while thinking about Bakushin quite a few times before…!

text_block_list.name: Sakura Bakushin O
text_block_list.text: Sometimes, even the gurus fail! Once again, let this be a lesson to you…!
